<html>
	<head>
		<title>This is the block editor dialog</title>
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Language" content="en-us">
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=windows-1252">
	</head>
	<body>
		<p><IMG alt="" src="kwedit.jpg"></p>
		<p>This is the editor dialog. With it you can edit the the keywords from the selected 
			keyword group.</p>
		<table border="1" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellPadding="1">
			<tr>
				<td width="35%">Editor control</td>
				<td width="65%">This control contains the keywords from the selected group displaying 
					them in the color which was selected for this group. Each line contains one 
					keyword. You can edit, remove and add keywords by simply editing the contents.
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td width="35%">OK</td>
				<td width="65%">Clicking on this button confirms the changes made.</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td width="35%">Cancel</td>
				<td width="65%">Clicking on this button cancels the changes made.</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
	</body>
</html>
